{"name": "test_etcd_ha_failover_vllm_aggregated", "status": "passed", "description": "\n    Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries.\n\n    This test:\n    1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n    2. Starts NATS, frontend, and a vLLM worker\n    3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n       - Terminate the replica by index\n       - Send inference request to verify system still works\n       - Restart the terminated node\n\n    This ensures testing of:\n    - ETCD leader termination\n    - Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n    ", "attachments": [{"name": "log", "source": "bd3855ba-6517-4635-8890-89f4435d43f1-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stdout", "source": "556f8739-0ae0-4ed8-8396-8fb8554439c1-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stderr", "source": "68042570-285b-4fc1-b000-545d42df4bcc-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}], "parameters": [{"name": "framework", "value": "'vllm'"}, {"name": "platform", "value": "'amd64'"}, {"name": "test_type", "value": "'pre_merge_gpu'"}], "start": 1775682835156, "stop": 1775682901922, "uuid": "6eecfd2a-5141-4837-a563-600c45735c0a", "historyId": "dc35b0086e1830ae22991aa0e74370ba", "testCaseId": "d55b1f5e2652b2d1788e47a10957ca38", "fullName": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha.test_vllm#test_etcd_ha_failover_vllm_aggregated", "labels": [{"name": "dynamo_workflow", "value": "Nightly CI Pipeline"}, {"name": "dynamo_framework", "value": "vllm"}, {"name": "dynamo_platform", "value": "amd64"}, {"name": "dynamo_testType", "value": "pre_merge_gpu"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "nightly"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "e2e"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "gpu_1"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "fault_tolerance"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "vllm"}, {"name": "parentSuite", "value": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha"}, {"name": "suite", "value": "test_vllm"}, {"name": "host", "value": "prod-tester-amd-gpu-v1-phg7c-runner-bskc5"}, {"name": "thread", "value": "83-MainThread"}